{"tid":2034881,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京全國揀選黨員到香港負責指導教學工作","createTime":"2020-05-25T13:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T01:24:23.000Z","uid":29188,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2b41da60b0c88e300028f66585d63dcac27400","tid":2034881,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0525a-05252020055046.html/BrainWash_mand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2Fwul0525a-05252020055046.html%2FBrainWash_mand.jpg&h=0f796745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><em>北京全國揀選黨員到香港負責指導教學工作</em></span><br />\n<br />\n北京對香港正式落實全面管治權，繼宣佈人大直接審議港版國安法後，教育部亦向多個省市下達指示，直接派出 「指導員」指導香港教師工作。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n多個省市已收到《關於遴選中小學及幼兒園教師赴港澳擔任教學指導教師的通知》。<br />\n<br />\n內容是選派選派優秀大陸教師赴港澳擔任教學指導教師。根據教育部工作安排，被揀選的教師必需 「政治立場堅定」、中共黨員。赴港澳擔任為期一年的教學指導工作。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>赴港澳教學指導教師的主要任務</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1．承擔香港或澳門中小學語文、數學等學科的教學指導及普通話教學工作；<br />\n<br />\n2．協助香港或澳門中小學推進校本課程建設；<br />\n<br />\n3．與香港或澳門幼兒園、中小學教師合作開展教學研究；<br />\n<br />\n4．促進內港與港澳兩地中小學、幼兒園的交流與合作。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n責編 胡力漢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0525a-05252020055046.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2Fwul0525a-05252020055046.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3oR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=c3edab53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/wul0525a-05252020055046.html</a>"},{"pid":"c657f3c4dedcb3f01be3e4c87580bd6082083de4","tid":2034881,"uid":29188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"直接換支那人教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf75b1d641dfc86cdbff869822e6931d2fa6e41","tid":2034881,"uid":15815,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:47:43.000Z","msg":"肯定大權過校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定好威威"},{"pid":"9915ca714c44bcb7d9d40d901c025ebe7d7eae24","tid":2034881,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"洗腦工作"},{"pid":"978e7c187c6c0baad66fe1bdb3c32bdcd13abacf","tid":2034881,"uid":292094,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"嚟到第一日已經比啲學生鏟到想走啦<br />\n喺office仲可能會經歷職場欺凌<br />\n除非換超過1/3 唔係嘅話存在感都係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18691227e1c369ab716246efa9ababba1f329bf1","tid":2034881,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"數學都要你指導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb176ee4048d7c6b2c1858c496f55151ec494e37","tid":2034881,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"978e7c187c6c0baad66fe1bdb3c32bdcd13abacf","tid":2034881,"uid":292094,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:51:31.000Z","msg":"嚟到第一日已經比啲學生鏟到想走啦<br />\n喺office仲可能會經歷職場欺凌<br />\n除非換超過1/3 唔係嘅話存在感都係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"好多中學都請落好多垃圾教普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d3a03c38f40d41728dc882b78c2eb493819343","tid":2034881,"uid":35254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"實比人欺凌番轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ac7a9a0977372d558413e9456321e2b844a2e0","tid":2034881,"uid":292094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb176ee4048d7c6b2c1858c496f55151ec494e37","tid":2034881,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"978e7c187c6c0baad66fe1bdb3c32bdcd13abacf","tid":2034881,"uid":292094,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"